### Ops Playbook API 验证脚本
### 使用方式：
### 1) 在 IDE 中打开本文件
### 2) 按顺序点击每个请求上方的 "Run"
### 3) 若启用鉴权，请在 Authorization 里填入 Bearer Token

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8079
@contentType = application/json
@batchNo = BATCH_20260323154550_3D693F7D
@dataId = eap-app.yml
@group = DEFAULT_GROUP
@namespace =
@submitter = ops_user
@ticketNo = OPS-TEST-001
@approver = ops_admin

### 1) 批次诊断
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ops/pipeline/diagnose
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "batchNo": "{{batchNo}}"
}

### 2) 配置预检（extraInfo 合并后）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ops/config/precheck
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "extraInfo": "{\"analysisEnabled\":true,\"maxImagesPerFile\":1,\"maxTotalAnalysisPages\":100}"
}

### 3) 生成变更计划（MCP 关闭时 nacosContext 可能不可用，属于预期）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ops/config/change-plan
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "namespace": "{{namespace}}",
  "group": "{{group}}",
  "dataId": "{{dataId}}",
  "extraInfo": "{\"analysisEnabled\":true}",
  "proposedChanges": {
    "eap.pipeline.analysis.max-images-per-file": 1,
    "eap.pipeline.scheduler.interval-ms": 60000
  }
}

### 4) 变更计划（反例：白名单外键，预期 decision=REJECT）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ops/config/change-plan
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "namespace": "{{namespace}}",
  "group": "{{group}}",
  "dataId": "{{dataId}}",
  "extraInfo": "{\"analysisEnabled\":true}",
  "proposedChanges": {
    "eap.pipeline.analysis.not-allowed-key": 123
  }
}

### 5) 提交审批（正例）
### 说明：从响应中复制 planId，填到下一条请求
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ops/config/submit-approval
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "namespace": "{{namespace}}",
  "group": "{{group}}",
  "dataId": "{{dataId}}",
  "extraInfo": "{\"analysisEnabled\":true}",
  "proposedChanges": {
    "eap.pipeline.analysis.max-images-per-file": 1
  },
  "submitter": "{{submitter}}",
  "ticketNo": "{{ticketNo}}"
}

### 6) 审批发布（将 <PLAN_ID> 替换为上一步返回的 planId）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ops/config/approve-publish
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "planId": "<PLAN_ID>",
  "approver": "{{approver}}",
  "comment": "test publish"
}

### 7) 提交审批（反例：越界值，预期 status=REJECTED）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ops/config/submit-approval
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "namespace": "{{namespace}}",
  "group": "{{group}}",
  "dataId": "{{dataId}}",
  "extraInfo": "{\"analysisEnabled\":true}",
  "proposedChanges": {
    "eap.pipeline.analysis.max-images-per-file": 999
  },
  "submitter": "{{submitter}}",
  "ticketNo": "OPS-TEST-002"
}

### 8) MCP 启用后建议再执行第 3、5、6 步
### 环境变量示例（重启应用后生效）：
### OPS_NACOS_MCP_ENABLED=true
### OPS_NACOS_MCP_BASE_URL=http://127.0.0.1:18080
### OPS_NACOS_MCP_TOKEN=<your-token-if-needed>
